ActCanada Cooperatives Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canada Cooperatives Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADA COOPERATIVES REGULATIONS in order to (1) better align service fees under the Canada Cooperatives Act (COOP ACT) with the cost of delivering the services; (2) promote compliance with the Coop Act; and (3) support greater corporate transparency.
